    "context": "\"This character has been chilled to the bone by cold. With their limbs frozen stiff, it takes a great deal of effort to move in a coordinated fashion. The effect will slowly wear off over [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + \"]\" + this.m.TurnsLeft + \"[/color] more turn(s).\""
